title: A review of Episode 1201 William Von Hippel
description:
William is a behavior psychologist and has just written a new book called “The Social Leap”. He and Joe talk in depth about what makes us do what we do and the road from Monkey in the trees to humans now. Get your note pads lads it's a fact loaded conversation. Really fun to review.

Enjoy my review folks!
